# Full dev loop (docs/WEB_UI.md): run with `just dev` (= hivemind Procfile.dev).
# daemon: air rebuilds (just build-bin) + restarts on Go/Rust/config saves
#         (.air.toml), serving the API on 127.0.0.1:8666 (--web on).
# web:    next dev serves the app on :3000 with HMR and proxies /api/* to
#         the daemon (next.config.ts).
# Browse http://localhost:3000/app/ for live-reloading UI work.
# ⚠ :8666 serves the web build EMBEDDED in the daemon binary — it never
#   auto-reloads (only `just build` refreshes it). Use :3000 during dev.
# If the daemon line dies instantly, air is probably not installed yet
# (`mise install`); hivemind then kills the web process too by design.
daemon: air
web: cd web && pnpm dev
